<a name="0">[0]</a> <a href="#0" id=0>As a scientific research area evolves, the knowledge flow network evolves with the citation network and behaves differently during different phases.</a>
<a name="1">[1]</a> <a href="#1" id=1>The development of a large knowledge flow network involves certain special roles shown in the accompanying table.</a>
<a name="2">[2]</a> <a href="#2" id=2>Scientists can publish in several areas, and thus be involved in different knowledge flow networks.</a>
<a name="3">[3]</a> <a href="#3" id=3>This enables knowledge to flow through knowledge networks in different areas to promote interdisciplinary research.</a>
